Inclusion Criteria:
- 53 teenagers, from Concarneau (France) high school, directly exposed from London terrorist attack (22.03.2017).
Exclusion Criteria:
- All persons not directly exposed;
- Relatives of teenagers;
- 3 physically injured teenagers.
